<b><i>c) I died twice to blues yesterday, both because I missed all 3 shots while they were coming in. I miss at least 1 shot per pull, no matter what the con now (yep, even green) and often miss 2 if the mob is blue... I haven't even bothered trying a yellow since the patch. </b></i><br>
